    "We treat each 3D patch of size 2 × 2 × 2 as a token in the 3D Swin Transformer.",
    "The 3D patch partitioning layer produces",
    "tokens, each with a 48-dimensional feature.",
    "A linear embedding layer then projects the features of each token to a higher dimension C (=128).",
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s42256-024-00824-8"
